snippet.textDisplay: I love this whole new take of Coke Studio on Indian music, away from all the typical north Indian Bollywood style of music to introducing people to the flavors of the south with all these different languages, genes, and fusions of music. It's just refreshing to listen to good music this is the reason why Coke Studio (pak) is such a big hit as they never shy from trying on new things and it's just something unique to that place and culture. this season of Coke Studio is just great I absolutely love it.
